        "html": "<div class=\"B1_text\">\n<p>　　一次,<a href=\"/remen/fayan.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">法眼</a>文益上堂说道:</p><p>　　“<a href=\"/remen/chujia.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">出家</a>人要依随时令而行,冷即冷,热即热。欲知<a href=\"/remen/foxing.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">佛性</a>之义,当观时节<a href=\"/remen/yinyuan1.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">因缘</a>。”</p> </div>"
